### 4. Preparing the Tableau Dataset

A final analysis table was created in BigQuery to simplify visualization in Tableau.

The dataset included:

- Cleaned cuisine categories
- Standardized price levels (`$`–`$$$$`)
- Customer ratings
- Review counts
- Geographic coordinates
- Restaurant metadata

This transformed the raw Yelp dataset into a single analysis-ready table optimized for dashboard development.
